<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yạ ạbny lạ tnsy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - yạ ạbny lạ tnsy sẖryʿty bl lyḥfẓ qlbk wṣạyạy

[V2]
 lạnhạ tdẖydk ṭwl ạyạm wsny ḥyạẗ ạyḍạaⁿ wslạm

[V3]
 1- twkl ʿly ạlrb bkl qlbk wʿly fhmk lạ tʿtmd

[V4]
 fy kl ṭrqk yạ ạbny ạʿrfẗ whw yqwm dạỷmạaⁿ sblk

[V5]
 lạ tkn ḥkymạ fy ʿyn nfsk ạtqy ạlrb wạbʿd ʿn ạlsẖr

[V6]
 wlạ tkrẗ ạbdạaⁿ yạ ạbny twbykẖẗ wtạdyb ạlrb lạ tḥtqr

[V7]
 2- ạlḥkmẗ hy ạlrạ̉s fạqtny ạlḥkmẗ wbkl mqtnạk ạqtny ạlfhm

[V8]
 ạ̉rfʿhạ ftʿlyk ạdẖạ ạʿtnqthạ tʿṭy lrạ̉sk ạ̉klyl nʿm

[V9]
 ạsmʿ yạ ạbny wạqbl ạqwạl fmy ftkwn ậmnạ dwmạaⁿ fy ạlṭryq

[V10]
 hdytk ạly̱ sbl ạlạstqạmẗ ạdẖạ srt fkẖṭwạtk lạ tḍyq

[V11]
 3- tmsk bạlạdb wlạ trkẖyẗ ạḥfẓẗ fạnẗ hw ḥyạtk

[V12]
 lạ tdkẖl fy ṭryq ạlạsẖrạr ạbtʿd ʿn ṭryqhm lslạmk

[V13]
 kl klmạt fmy hy bạlḥq wạ̉fttạḥ sẖfty dạỷmạaⁿ ạstqạmẗ

[V14]
 lạn fmy ylhj bạlṣdq wtạdyby ạḥsn mn ạlfḍẗ ạlmkẖtạrẗ</lyrics>
<author>ʿạdl ḥbyb, ʿạdl ḥbyb</author>
